<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/gordon-frisby> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Gordon Frisby is an accomplished global Finance Director with over 25 years of senior management experience. His career began at BDO Binder before moving to Black & Decker Corporation in Germany and Switzerland, where he spent 16 years in various senior finance roles. Prior to joining Nuclear Restoration Services (NRS), he served as Chief Financial Officer at NSK Europe, overseeing finance, information systems, and legal functions. Gordon is also a non-executive director for Wealth Management and a chartered member of ACCA."@en .
